1 - activate the extension following the standard eZ Publish procedures
    (remember to regenerate the ezp_extension.php autoload file)

2 - clear the template cache


3 - configure ezgoogletranslate.ini.append.php for the desired translation provider
  . you will need a free Azure key for microsoft translator. See: http://www.microsofttranslator.com
  . the googletranslate key is otoh pay for: http://code.google.com/apis/language/translate/overview.html
